      <title>1840 Dec. 16, Nashville [Tennessee] [to] A. Fergusson, Carthage, Tenn[essee] / Geo. Harris</title>
   </titleInfo>
   <abstract>This is a letter from George Harris to Adam Fergusson, dated December 16, 1840. Harris thanks Fergusson for extending the circulation of the newspaper The Union. Harris plans to use the paper to promote Republican doctrine. He mentions some political opinions.</abstract>
